data.description: Welcome to this charming three bedroom two bathroom home! This property is perfect for anyone looking to purchase a home or those looking to make an investment. With a beautiful backyard and recent updates, this home offers a wonderful opportunity to create your dream living space. Don't miss out on the chance to see everything this home has to offer. Seller's will contribute $5000 towards closing cost. Schedule a visit today and let your imagination run wild with the possibilities!!!
